                    h5 Career Skill Choice
                    p Careers include choices of career skills. Careers include starting equipment and can be a prerequisite for talents. 
                    p #[strong Thoughts:] Some GMs just allow for ad-hoc careers, since the only thing they generate is career skills, treating setting careers as suggestions. R.A.W. careers don't allow for any choice, even though the concept might work with Brawl instead of Melee, etc. This strikes a happy medium for me - choices of career skills where an archetype might allow for different options, but still structured enough to allow for prerequisite talents and trees and so forth.
